name: Starcraft 2 | Nova
description:
This LoRA is trained with 151 images, varying from cosplays to fan arts, of StarCraft 2's Nova.

Simply load up your favorite model and use <lora:starcraft2Nova_20:1> for this lora to take effect!

This LoRA was trained using SD 1.5 and therefore may not work with all models!

For early access and custom LoRA's consider joining my patreon! https://patreon.com/Crazygirlashleyy

Preview Images made using:
Crazygirlashley-mix-2

anime_cyriousmix_14

animated_xperoEnd1essModel_v1
kotosmix_v10

modelVersions.description: Increased training sample images from 9 to 151. More direct training on the character/outfit. Less effect on background around image
